and, as it turned out, frostbite.</p>

<p>For Doug Scott, it was the fulfilment of a fortune-tellerâ€™s prophesy given to his mother:
that her eldest son would be in danger in a high place with the whole world watching.</p>

<p>Scott and Haston returned home national heroes with their image splashed across the front
